name: Global Blessed Land: I Can Add Attributes On The Buildings
summary:
Synopsis

After each person reached the age, he or she could open his or her own blessed land.
B0XNʘVEL.C0M

The blessed land was bestowed by the will of heaven and earth.
Within the blessed land, one could cultivate dao soldiers, breed all things, or create supreme imperial dynasties.
The world was shattered into countless pieces, forming countless star gates, with three kingdoms, a martial world, immortals and gods, and demons.




There were martial arts from the world of martial arts, immortal laws from the world of immortals, and technological things beyond reality.
Mei Changge accidentally opened his own Point-adding System and found that he could add it not only to himself but also to the buildings that belonged to him.
Broken Village +10086= Eternal Heaven!
Black Earth +10010= Nine Heavens Resting Soil!
Archery Tower +9527= Divine Demon Crossbow of the Heavens!

Global Blessed Land: I Can Add Attributes On The Buildings
author: Pond Fish In October
